At Truro, we set our algorithm
a goal -

49:15.840 --> 49:19.480
to turn Alfonsi's fortunes around.

49:20.720 --> 49:22.240
NEWS JINGLE PLAYS

49:22.240 --> 49:24.200
TRANSLATION:

49:33.320 --> 49:36.200
An alternative portrait
