a different Tbilisi.

50:29.720 --> 50:32.000
Here was a city at war

50:32.000 --> 50:34.680
divided over a number
of burning issues.

50:34.680 --> 50:37.160
Looking deeper, data revealed

50:37.160 --> 50:40.640
exactly which issues caused
most concern,

50:40.640 --> 50:44.840
which news stories literally kept
the locals awake at night.

50:52.200 --> 50:53.920
The silent majority

50:53.920 --> 50:55.720
had suddenly been spoken for.

50:55.720 --> 50:59.280
"The real people of Tbilisi"
began to trend,

50:59.280 --> 51:01.360
spawning a movement, a base.

51:01.360 --> 51:04.400
CHANTING: Alfonsi! Alfonsi!

51:04.400 --> 51:08.480
Alfonsi was a rising star of
the populist right.

51:10.800 --> 51:12.720
Or so it seemed.

51:12.720 --> 51:15.480
